_sText: Its remake of awp_ruins_final for CS:S Improvments: + Nodraw + Hints (fps improvement) + HDR (Cubemaps + ToneMap) + Now 64 Spawns + .nav file - Some details (you wouldn't see it, because they were under map) Also now awps dont lie on the respawn.
